==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*ἄρχομαι / archomai / ar'-khom-ahee

===Etymology===
*Middle voice of [[ἄρχω]] {{GG|757}} (through the implication of precedence); 

===Verb===
'''ἄρχομαι'''

# To [[commence]] (in order of time): - rehearse from the) [[begin]] (-ning).

